  <h2>AI Engineering Roadmap</h2>

  <p>
    I'm a software engineer with a cloud data engineering background
    across Java, Python, and the GCP stack. I'm currently pursuing UT
    Austin's online MSAI program, starting Fall 2026 and targeting
    graduation in May 2028.
  </p>
  <p>
    I already work across data and cloud engineering, and I know how to
    build reliable systems in production. Now I'm adding the ML, AI, and
    mathematical depth to operate higher up the stack. The goal is to grow
    into a senior engineering role and become the engineer trusted to
    design, scale, and own serious systems.
  </p>
  <p>Here's the plan, broken into three phases.</p>

  <h2>Phase 1: Foundation</h2>

